                    "name": "Activate",
                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "action_type": {
                        "type": "stat_block_section",
                        "subtype": "action_type",
                        "name": "Two Actions"
                    },
                    "frequency": "once per day",
                    "effect": "With three sharp taps on the ground, the *Staff of the Ruling Beast* casts *bullhorn* as a 5th-rank cantrip, affecting you so long as you hold the staff. While affected, you can make your words rumble with palpable force, allowing creatures (including those who cannot hear) to feel your speech and identify your location as if they were using an imprecise sense.",
                    "links": [
                        {
                            "type": "link",
                            "name": "bullhorn",
                            "alt": "bullhorn",
                            "game-obj": "Spells",
                            "aonid": 1971
                        }
                    ],
                    "traits": [
                        {
                            "name": "Auditory",
                            "type": "trait",
                            "alternate_link": {
                                "type": "alternate_link",
                                "game-obj": "Traits",
                                "aonid": 16,
                                "alternate_type": "legacy"
                            },
                            "edition": "remastered",
                            "sources": [
                                {
                                    "type": "source",
                                    "name": "Player Core",
                                    "link": {
                                        "type": "link",
                                        "name": "Player Core pg. 453",
                                        "alt": "Player Core pg. 453",
                                        "game-obj": "Sources",
                                        "aonid": 216
                                    },
                                    "page": 453,
                                    "errata": {
                                        "type": "link",
                                        "name": "2.0",
                                        "alt": "2.0",
                                        "game-obj": "Sources",
                                        "aonid": 216
                                    }
                                }
                            ],
                            "game-obj": "Traits",
                            "game-id": "84c09922ddd30f2144494f2cb6f19412",
                            "text": "Auditory actions and effects rely on sound. An action with the auditory trait can be successfully performed only if the creature using the action can speak or otherwise produce the required sounds. A spell or effect with the auditory trait has its effect only if the target can hear it. This applies only to sound-based parts of the effect, as determined by the GM. This is different from a sonic effect, which still affects targets who can\u2019t hear it (such as deaf targets) as long as the effect itself makes sound."
                        },
                        {
                            "name": "Manipulate",
                            "type": "trait",
                            "alternate_link": {
                                "type": "alternate_link",
                                "game-obj": "Traits",
                                "aonid": 104,
                                "alternate_type": "legacy"
                            },
                            "edition": "remastered",
                            "sources": [
                                {
                                    "type": "source",
                                    "name": "Player Core",
                                    "link": {
                                        "type": "link",
                                        "name": "Player Core pg. 458",
                                        "alt": "Player Core pg. 458",
                                        "game-obj": "Sources",
                                        "aonid": 216
                                    },
                                    "page": 458,
                                    "errata": {
                                        "type": "link",
                                        "name": "2.0",
                                        "alt": "2.0",
                                        "game-obj": "Sources",
                                        "aonid": 216
                                    }
                                }
                            ],
                            "game-obj": "Traits",
                            "game-id": "6a0bf3cdfe7c0fc427c7b8ea9310f113",
                            "text": "You must physically manipulate an item or make gestures to use an action with this trait. Creatures without a suitable appendage can\u2019t perform actions with this trait. Manipulate actions often trigger reactions."
                        }
                    ],
                    "activation_name": "Overwhelming Sound"
